Description:
A luxury modern statement in Yarra’s Edge
An array of stunning highlights awaits one lucky buyer on the 25th floor of this luxury Docklands building, with this 2 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom residence promising a level of quality that is second to none plus astonishing CBD and water views that you will never get tired of.
The ‘Array’ complex in the Yarra’s Edge precinct is the setting for this contemporary haven. The exceptional views of the marina below and CBD buildings in the distance will be the first thing you notice, with the large covered balcony the ideal vantage point for the views as you sit back with a wine and enjoy the warm summer breeze.
The central living zone consists of areas to lounge and dine, with the adjoining kitchen equipped with stone surfaces, the convenience of an island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master retreat has a large built-in robe and chic dual vanity ensuite, meanwhile also be impressed by the sizeable 2nd bedroom, a study room or potential 3rd bedroom, main bathroom, separate laundry/ storage room, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces.
Enjoy exclusive access to on-site gym & residence lounge, plus the fantastic RekDek facilities which include a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. You’re near DFO Shopping and South Wharf Promenade which enjoys terrific bars and eateries including The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard, Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Melbourne’s lively CBD, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Insights: 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Sleek renovated charm and river views to truly appreciate
From the startling marina views to the expansive space and alluring contemporary class which can be attributed to a sleek renovation, this generous two bedroom, two bathroom Docklands stunner is enhanced by a spacious covered balcony for those who love outdoor entertaining!
Relax in style in this 18th floor retreat, which has an enormous central lounge and dining zone which promises beautiful timber flooring underfoot. The wonderful designer kitchen adjoins the central living area and comes with sumptuous stone benches and splashback, feature island bench, wine storage, and stainless steel appliances. The main zone further opens out to the balcony which has stunning Yarra River and Bolte Bridge views.
A master bedroom includes access to its own private balcony area as well as ample built-in robes and a dazzling double vanity ensuite. The 2nd bedroom with BIRs also has entry to the main balcony. Other property features include a central bathroom, a separated laundry room/ storage, ducted heating and cooling throughout, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. The property also has a total of 123 sqm (approx.) of space inside and out.
In the Yarra’s Edge precinct, you’re close to the brilliant South Wharf Promenade which has a variety of sensational bars and restaurants plus easy access to DFO shopping. You’re also a short trip to Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and public transport.
Insights: 1805/50 Lorimer Street, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2018 and 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
A Serrata entertainer that promises style and space
With 105 sqm (approx.) of total space including a fantastic wraparound balcony which promises relaxed alfresco options all year round and terrific views, this modern and stylish two bedroom corner apartment is an exceptional 12th floor offering in the prime Serrata complex.
This apartment is located in the heart of the Victoria Harbour precinct. A sizeable central living zone has an open feel and will cater for all your everyday living desires from casual meals to lounging in front of the TV after dinner. The adjoining stone kitchen is an easy care space equipped with stainless steel appliances including an induction cooktop and dishwasher.
The bright master bedroom includes its very own sleek ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom is placed right next to the quality bathroom. The generous balcony is ideal for outdoor dinners and morning coffees, while further embrace a European laundry, wall heating, built-in robes in both bedrooms, secure intercom entry, and a secure car space.
Walk to some of the Docklands best cafes and restaurants including Banoi Docklands, Taberu-Ya, and Pok Pok, while also enjoy nearby attractions including Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Woolworths supermarket, community garden, and trams on Harbour Esplanade.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
With great returns, this 2 bed, 2 bath apartment has fantastic views of the CBD, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
This apartment is completed by split system heating & cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.

Rare Waterfront Dream Home Available
Encompassing luxury features this spacious two bedroom, two bathroom apartment is perfectly positioned on the 12th floor of the sought after Convesso' complex in Docklands with north facing views. Description:
Stunning Marina Views
Bathed in natural light with captivating views across the Marina all the way to the Bolte and across Port Philip Bay is this spacious immaculate apartment in Mirvac's Tower 2 in the wonderful and most sought after Yarra's Edge precinct.
Offering the discerning buyer the comforts of 2 generous size bedrooms, master with triple robes and en-suite with a separate shower, second main bathroom, large living/dining adjoining kitchen with quality stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops and ample cupboard space. Other features include floor to ceiling windows, fabulous balcony providing magnificent outlook across the Yarra all the way to the Bolte perfect for entertaining guests, 2 secure under cover car spaces and resident access to the fabulous Rek Dek facilities which include a heated indoor lap pool, spa, sauna, steam-room and gymnasium.
The building is within walking distance to South Wharf, DFO and all the beauty that Yarra's Edge has to offer.
Inspection is sure to impress.

The exceptional private balcony will be ideal in the warmer months for alfresco meals as you soak in the astonishing city and river vistas, while the bedroom (BIRs) neighbours a study nook and contemporary kitchen with large shower.
Further enjoying ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to building facilities including a gymnasium and heated pool, this retreat is in close proximity to South Wharf restaurants, DFO shopping, Etihad Stadium, CBD attractions, and public transport.

Description:
Podium Apartment with Low Owner’s Corporate Fees
This podium apartment shows off the Yarra River as well as a gorgeous leafy aspect that will be your scenic backdrop 24 hours a day, this modern, stylish and charming two bedroom waterfront apartment in Yarra’s Edge is simply stunning.
Located in Exclusive 64 River Esplanade, Docklands with only 6 properties in the block and 2 apartments per floor, you will enjoy the convenience of having a car space on the same floor as your apartment.
This outstanding floorplan allows for both bedrooms, each with BIRs, to be located at the front and rear of the apartment providing maximum privacy. Both bedrooms also enjoy direct access to the north-facing entertainers balcony which runs the full length of the apartment.
Timber floors are featured in the bright living and dining zone, while the tiled kitchen has impeccable storage, glass splashback, stone benchtops and stainless steel appliances. Other features include a deluxe bathroom, European laundry, ducted heat/cool, secure intercom, car space and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, sauna, steam room, & sun deck.
Yarra’s Edge is the most sought-after location in the Docklands thanks to its position near amazing South Wharf attractions including DFO shopping and restaurants/bars including The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard, just to name a few. You’re also close to Crown Entertainment Complex, Melbourne’s bustling CBD, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Description:
FANTASTIC VIEWS FROM FABULOUS APARTMENT
Delivering spectacular views from the 12th floor of the sought after Nolan Complex is this 90sqm apartment in New Quay. Comprising of 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 car spaces, this Docklands dwelling possesses space and elegance.
The generous living area opens up onto balcony with stunning views – perfect for alfresco dining or a refreshing beverage at the end of the day. The stylish kitchen comes complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, and stone bench-top island breakfast bar.
The large master bedroom boasts a walk-in-robe, and a chic, modern en-suite. The second bedroom is also generous in size, and includes plenty of storage with its built in robes. Both bedrooms have balcony access with loads of natural light.
The central bathroom completes this fantastic apartment with its clean, contemporary finishes, ample storage, and separate bath and shower.
Euro-laundry, central heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, 2 car spaces, and a large storage cage round out this immaculate inner-city pad.
Typical of modern apartment living, additional facilities for residents include a fully equipped gym and heated pool. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Both generously sized bedrooms include mirrored built-in robes, and both come with plenty of natural light. The the main bathroom and ensuite are sleek & modern, and have an abundance of cupboard space.
A Euro-laundry, split system heating/cooling, modern fixtures & fittings, a secure car park, and secure swipe/intercom entry complete this elegant Docklands home.
Typical of modern apartment living, this property comes with a pool, sauna, gym, tennis court, and library for use by all residents. Wonderfully situated close to public transport, and with an array of waterside restaurants and world class shopping on your doorstep, this must see home is also only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
A Point in the Right Direction
A glorious 2 bedroom apartment awaits the discerning buyer, either to move in or rent out straight away. Located in the renowned Elenberg Fraser Watergate residential complex, its’ central location is perfect. With the quietest living around due to its unique aerodynamic tower design, come and see why so many residents love living here!
Beautifully spacious apartment with large open plan dining and living area adjoins East facing balcony to take in the City skyline views. Across to the South you will be greeted with picturesque views over Docklands Park. A stylish kitchen with stone bench tops incorporates an island bench, great for food preparation, as well as integrated stainless steel appliances including Gas stove, electric oven and dishwasher. Main bedroom with ensuite and study alcove. Mirrored built in robes to both bedrooms. Fully tiled Central dual access bathroom with laundry area.
Additional features to this lovely apartment include: ducted heating and cooling, secured entrance, onsite building manager, double glazed floor to ceiling windows and cross ventilation, one undercover car space.
Building facilities include: 3 lane heated lap pool with spa, gymnasium, sauna and function room.
This is a wonderful opportunity to live right in the heart of Docklands, close to Southern Cross Station, located within the Free Tram Zone, walking distance to an abundance of great cafes and restaurants, and everything you could possibly need.
